title: Allowing in New Members
body: Formerly, more members were part of this collective but several took back their ETH. Only members who stayed were given FUCD coins and are given the ability to vote and the chance to join in on collective NFT Buy-ins. Should we let more members of FU into this DAO?
choices: No, keep the limits as they are.
